---
title: CI/CD Pipeline
description: Continuous Integration and Deployment pipeline for Hospeda
author: Tech Team
date: 2025-11-06
---

```mermaid
graph LR
    %% Trigger
    Trigger([🚀 Git Push])

    %% GitHub Actions - CI Phase
    subgraph GitHubActions[⚙️ GitHub Actions CI]
        Checkout[📥 Checkout Code<br/>actions/checkout@v4]
        SetupNode[🟢 Setup Node.js 20<br/>actions/setup-node@v4]
        SetupPNPM[📦 Setup PNPM<br/>pnpm/action-setup@v2]
        Install[📦 Install Dependencies<br/>pnpm install --frozen-lockfile]
        Lint[🧹 Lint<br/>pnpm lint]
        TypeCheck[🔍 Type Check<br/>pnpm typecheck]
        Test[🧪 Run Tests<br/>pnpm test:coverage]
        Build[🏗️ Build Apps<br/>pnpm build]
        CIPassed{✅ All Checks<br/>Passed?}
    end

    %% Failure Path
    Fail[❌ Pipeline Failed]
    Notify[📧 Notify Team<br/>GitHub Notification]
    FixIssues[🔧 Fix Issues]

    %% Success Path - Branch Detection
    BranchDetect{🌳 Branch?}

    %% Preview Deployment
    subgraph VercelPreview[🔍 Vercel Preview Deployment]
        PreviewBuild[🏗️ Build Preview]
        PreviewMigrate[🔄 Run Migrations<br/>Preview DB]
        PreviewDeploy[🚀 Deploy to Preview]
        PreviewURL[🔗 Generate Preview URL]
        PreviewComment[💬 Comment on PR]
    end

    %% Production Deployment
    subgraph VercelProduction[🚀 Vercel Production Deployment]
        ProdBuild[🏗️ Build Production]
        ProdMigrate[🔄 Run Migrations<br/>Production DB]
        ProdDeploy[🚀 Deploy to Production]
        ProdURL[🔗 Update Production URL]
        ProdVerify[✅ Verify Deployment]
    end

    %% Post-Deployment
    subgraph PostDeployment[📊 Post-Deployment]
        HealthCheck[🏥 Health Check<br/>/api/health]
        SmokeTests[🧪 Smoke Tests]
        Monitoring[📈 Start Monitoring]
        Logs[📝 Check Logs]
    end

    %% Deployment Status
    DeploySuccess{✅ Deploy<br/>Success?}
    DeployFailed[❌ Deployment Failed]
    Rollback[↩️ Auto Rollback<br/>Previous Version]
    Alert[🚨 Alert Team]
    Done([✨ Complete])

    %% Flow
    Trigger --> Checkout
    Checkout --> SetupNode
    SetupNode --> SetupPNPM
    SetupPNPM --> Install
    Install --> Lint
    Lint --> TypeCheck
    TypeCheck --> Test
    Test --> Build
    Build --> CIPassed

    CIPassed -->|No ✗| Fail
    Fail --> Notify
    Notify --> FixIssues
    FixIssues -.->|Push Again| Trigger

    CIPassed -->|Yes ✓| BranchDetect

    %% Branch Routing
    BranchDetect -->|PR/Feature| PreviewBuild
    PreviewBuild --> PreviewMigrate
    PreviewMigrate --> PreviewDeploy
    PreviewDeploy --> PreviewURL
    PreviewURL --> PreviewComment
    PreviewComment --> DeploySuccess

    BranchDetect -->|Main| ProdBuild
    ProdBuild --> ProdMigrate
    ProdMigrate --> ProdDeploy
    ProdDeploy --> ProdURL
    ProdURL --> ProdVerify
    ProdVerify --> DeploySuccess

    %% Post-Deployment Flow
    DeploySuccess -->|Yes ✓| HealthCheck
    HealthCheck --> SmokeTests
    SmokeTests --> Monitoring
    Monitoring --> Logs
    Logs --> Done

    DeploySuccess -->|No ✗| DeployFailed
    DeployFailed --> Rollback
    Rollback --> Alert
    Alert --> FixIssues

    %% Pipeline Steps Detail
    subgraph PipelineSteps[Pipeline Steps Detail]
        Step1[1️⃣ Code Quality<br/>Lint + TypeCheck]
        Step2[2️⃣ Testing<br/>Unit + Integration]
        Step3[3️⃣ Build<br/>Compile TypeScript]
        Step4[4️⃣ Deploy<br/>Vercel Edge]
        Step5[5️⃣ Verify<br/>Health Checks]
    end

    %% Environment Variables
    subgraph EnvVars[🔐 Environment Variables]
        DevEnv[Development<br/>.env.local]
        PreviewEnv[Preview<br/>Vercel Env]
        ProdEnv[Production<br/>Vercel Env]
    end

    BranchDetect -.->|Load| EnvVars

    %% Styling
    classDef trigger fill:#3b82f6,stroke:#1e40af,color:#fff
    classDef ci fill:#10b981,stroke:#059669,color:#fff
    classDef preview fill:#f59e0b,stroke:#d97706,color:#fff
    classDef production fill:#8b5cf6,stroke:#7c3aed,color:#fff
    classDef postdeploy fill:#06b6d4,stroke:#0891b2,color:#fff
    classDef failure fill:#ef4444,stroke:#dc2626,color:#fff
    classDef success fill:#22c55e,stroke:#16a34a,color:#fff
    classDef decision fill:#6b7280,stroke:#4b5563,color:#fff

    class Trigger trigger
    class Checkout,SetupNode,SetupPNPM,Install,Lint,TypeCheck,Test,Build ci
    class PreviewBuild,PreviewMigrate,PreviewDeploy,PreviewURL,PreviewComment preview
    class ProdBuild,ProdMigrate,ProdDeploy,ProdURL,ProdVerify production
    class HealthCheck,SmokeTests,Monitoring,Logs postdeploy
    class Fail,Notify,FixIssues,DeployFailed,Rollback,Alert failure
    class Done success
    class CIPassed,BranchDetect,DeploySuccess decision
```
